                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="bg-yellow-600 text-white p-2 rounded-full mr-4">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">Participer à la lutte pour la Santé pour tous, pour la prise en charge et la protection des personnes atteintes du VIH/SIDA, du paludisme et toutes autres maladies</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 hover-scale">
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="bg-yellow-600 text-white p-2 rounded-full mr-4">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
